title: Episode 244: Limp Dick (Feat. Fivio Foreign)
itunes:title: Episode 244: Limp Dick (Feat. Fivio Foreign)
description:
Rapper, Fivio Foreign, opens up about his time in quarantine. He redefines “viral,” talks shit to 14-year-olds on video games, and even admits he once had an STD… Make sure to check out his new project, 800 B.C. Enjoy!
